2700.name: Dieter's Key
2700.description: A key to the chest where Dieter has hidden the Scriptures of Knowledge. Take this to Astrologer Creta in Floran Village.

2701.name: Creta's 2nd Letter
2701.description: Creta's letter describing the theft of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Take this to Magister Dieter in the Town of Giran.

2702.name: Dieter's Letter
2702.description: A letter from Magister Dieter to Trader Edroc of the weapons shop of Hunters Village.

2703.name: Dieter's Diary
2703.description: Magister Dieter's Diary, given by him in hopes that it may be of aid in recovering the Scriptures of Knowledge.

2704.name: Raut's Letter Envelope
2704.description: A plain letter envelope with no contents. The envelope is addressed "To Warehouse Keeper Raut".

2705.name: Triff's Ring
2705.description: A ring given by Drunkard Triff. Show this ring to those whom Triff has entrusted with the Scriptures of Knowledge.

2706.name: Scripture Chapter 1
2706.description: The 1st book of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Gather all 4 books.

2707.name: Scripture Chapter 2
2707.description: The 2nd book of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Gather all 4 books.

2708.name: Scripture Chapter 3
2708.description: The 3rd book of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Gather all 4 books.

2709.name: Scripture Chapter 4
2709.description: The 4th book of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Gather all 4 books.

2710.name: Valkon's Request
2710.description: Warehouse Keeper Valkon's request. The instructions are to bring back the crystal of purity.

2711.name: Poitan's Notes
2711.description: Blacksmith Poitan's accounting books. Take this to Elder Casian of the Wastelands.

2712.name: Scriptures of Knowledge
2712.description: A scripture edited by Elder Cronos. It is said to contain a vast knowledge of the past. It is part of a 4-scripture set.

2713.name: Strong Liquor
2713.description: As its name indicates, a strong liquor. Take this to Drunkard Triff at the harbor.

2714.name: Crystal of Purity
2714.description: An item that Warehouse Keeper Valkon in Town of Giran agreed to trade with you for scripture chapter 2.

2715.name: Casian's List
2715.description: 10 ghoul's skins, 12 units of medusa's blood, 5 units of fettered soul's ichor, and 5 enchanted gargoyle's nails.

2716.name: Ghoul's Skin
2716.description: The skin of a ghoul. Gather 10 of these and take them to Elder Casian.

2717.name: Medusa's Blood
2717.description: Medusa's Blood. Gather 12 bottles and take them to Elder Casian.

2718.name: Fettered Soul's Ichor
2718.description: The ichor of a fettered soul. Gather 5 units and take them to Elder Casian.

2719.name: Enchanted Gargoyle's Nail
2719.description: The enchanted nails of a gargoyle. Gather 5 of these and take them to Elder Casian.

2720.name: Symbol of Cronos
2720.description: The mark of Cronos, the top sage of the continent. Take this to Magister Mirien in the Town of Dion.

2721.name: Mark of Pilgrim
2721.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Pilgrim. An occupation change related item.

2722.name: Book of Sage
2722.description: A book received from Elder Casian. Take this book to Hermit Santiago.

2723.name: Voucher of Trial
2723.description: A mark given by Hermit Santiago. Show this to Seer Tanapi of the Orc Village.

2724.name: Spirit of Flame
2724.description: Proof that you have an understanding of the spirit of flame. In order to carry out the next stage of this trial, go see Gauri Twinklerock of Dwarven Village.

2725.name: Essence of Flame
2725.description: A jewel obtained from the lava salamander. Take this to the Ancestor Martankus.

2726.name: Book of Gerald
2726.description: A book given by Priest Gerald. The book looks very cheap.

2727.name: Gray Badge
2727.description: A badge given by Wanderer Dorf. Take this to Priest Primos at Town of Giran.

2728.name: Picture of Nahir
2728.description: A picture of the monster, Nahir. Defeat Nahir, who lurks in the depths of the Elven Ruins on Talking Island.

2729.name: Hair of Nahir
2729.description: The hair of the monster, Nahir. Take this to Priest Petron.

2730.name: Statue of Einhasad
2730.description: A statue of Einhasad given by Priest Petron. Take this to Andellia, who lives near the Mother Tree Glade in the Elven Village.

2731.name: Book of Darkness
2731.description: A book given by Uruha. The book contains unrecognizable letters written in blood.

2732.name: Debris of Willow
2732.description: Debris obtained from the black willow. Go and seek Uruha while in possession of this.

2733.name: Tag of Rumor
2733.description: This contains rumors regarding Wanderer Dorf and Priest Gerald.

2734.name: Mark of Trust
2734.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Trust. An occupation change related item.

2735.name: Letter to Elf
2735.description: A letter requesting the trust of the Elves. Deliver this to Hierarch Asterios of the Elven Village.

2736.name: Letter to Dark Elf
2736.description: A letter requesting the trust of the Dark Elves. Deliver this to Tetrarch Thifiell of the Dark Elven Village.

2737.name: Letter to Dwarf
2737.description: A letter requesting the trust of the Dwarves. Deliver this to Lockirin of the Dwarven Village.

2738.name: Letter to Orc
2738.description: A letter requesting the trust of the Orcs. Deliver this to the Pa'agrio Lord Kakai at the Orc Village.

2739.name: Letter to Seresin
2739.description: A letter given by High Priest Hollint. Deliver this to Cardinal Seresin at the Town of Oren.

2740.name: Scroll of Dark Elf Trust
2740.description: A scroll given by Tetrarch Thifiell. Deliver this, along with the scroll of the Elf trust, to High Priest Hollint.

2741.name: Scroll of Elf Trust
2741.description: This item can be obtained from Hierarch Asterios. Give this item along with scroll of Dark Elf trust to High Priest Hollint.

2742.name: Scroll of Dwarf Trust
2742.description: A scroll given by Lockirin of the Iron Gate. Deliver this, along with the scroll of Orc trust, to Cardinal Seresin.

2743.name: Scroll of Orc Trust
2743.description: A scroll given by Kakai, Lord of Flame. Deliver this, along with the scroll of Dwarf trust, to Cardinal Seresin.

2744.name: Recommendation of Hollint
2744.description: Deliver this to High Priest Biotin at the Temple of Einhasad on Talking Island.

2745.name: Order of Asterios
2745.description: Slay Luell of Zephyr Winds and Actea of Verdant Wilds and bring back proof of their deaths.

2746.name: Breath of Winds
2746.description: Obtained from Luell of Zephyr Winds. Deliver this, along with the seed of verdure to Hierarch Asterios.

2747.name: Seed of Verdure
2747.description: A proof obtained from Actea of Verdant Wilds. Deliver this, along with the breath of winds, to Hierarch Asterios.

2748.name: Letter from Thifiell
2748.description: Deliver this to Magister Clayton, member of the Dark Elf Guild, in the Town of Dion.

2749.name: Guardian Basilisk Blood
2749.description: Blood taken from a Guardian Basilisk. Collect 5 to produce Basilisk Plasma.

2750.name: Giant Aphid
2750.description: Acquired from various Ant Soldiers. Collect 5 to create Honey Dew.

2751.name: Stakatos Fluids
2751.description: Fluid acquired from various Marsh Stakatos. Collect 5 to produce Stakato Ichor.

2752.name: Basilisk Plasma
2752.description: Take this, along with the honey dew and stakato ichor, to Magister Clayton.

2753.name: Honey Dew
2753.description: Take this, along with the basilisk plasma and stakato ichor, to Magister Clayton.

2754.name: Stakato Ichor
2754.description: Take this, along with the honey dew and basilisk plasma, to Magister Clayton.

2755.name: Order of Clayton
2755.description: Obtain basilisk plasma of a guardian basilisk, stakato ichor of a marsh stakato and honey dew of an ant guard and take them to Magister Clayton.

2756.name: Parasite of Lota
2756.description: This may be obtained from the Windsus. Gather 10 of these and take them to Seer Manakia.

2757.name: Letter to Manakia
2757.description: A letter received from Pa'agrio Lord Kakai. Deliver this to Seer Manakia in the Town of Giran.

2758.name: Letter of Manakia
2758.description: A letter received from Seer Manakia. Deliver this to Pa'agrio Lord Kakai.

2759.name: Letter to Nikola
2759.description: A letter received from Lockirin of the Iron Gate. Deliver this to Maestro Nikola of the Cruma Tower.

2760.name: Order of Nikola
2760.description: Obtain 1 Porta Heartstone and take it to Maestro Nikola.

2761.name: Heartstone of Porta
2761.description: Heartstone acquired from Porta. Bring it to Maestro Nikola.

2762.name: Mark of Duelist
2762.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Duelist. An item for occupational change.

2763.name: Order Gludio
2763.description: Kill at least 10 punchers and 10 noble ant leaders in Gludio.

2764.name: Order Dion
2764.description: Kill at least 10 marsh stakato drones and 10 dead seekers in Dion.

2765.name: Order Giran
2765.description: Kill at least 10 Breka orc overlords and 10 fettered souls in Giran.

2766.name: Order Oren
2766.description: Kill at least 10 Leto lizardman overlords and 10 enchanted monster eyes in Oren.

2767.name: Order Aden
2767.description: Kill at least 10 Tamlin orcs and 10 Tamlin orc archers in Aden.

2768.name: Puncher's Shard
2768.description: A shard of the broken puncher. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2769.name: Noble Ant's Feeler
2769.description: The feelers of the noble ant leader. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2770.name: Drone's Chitin
2770.description: The chitin of the marsh stakato drone. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2771.name: Dead Seeker Fang
2771.description: The fangs of the dead seeker bat. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2772.name: Overlord Necklace
2772.description: Collect ten Breka orc overlord's necklaces and take them to Duelist Kaien.

2773.name: Fettered Soul's Chain
2773.description: The chains that surround a fettered soul's body. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2774.name: Chief's Amulet
2774.description: The amulet of a Leto lizardman overlord. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2775.name: Enchanted Monster Eye Meat
2775.description: The flesh of an enchanted eye. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2776.name: Tamlin Orc's Ring
2776.description: The ring of a Tamlin orc. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2777.name: Tamlin Orc's Arrow
2777.description: The arrows of a Tamlin orc archer. Collect 10 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2778.name: Final Order
2778.description: Defeat the Excuro and Krator of the Cruma Tower, the Grandis of Giran, the Timak Orc Overlord of Oren, and the Lakin of Aden 3 times.

2779.name: Excuro's Skin
2779.description: The skin of the excuro. Collect 3 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2780.name: Krator's Shard
2780.description: The shard of a broken krator. Collect 3 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2781.name: Grandis' Skin
2781.description: The skin of a grandis. Collect 3 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2782.name: Timak Orc's Belt
2782.description: The belt of a Timak orc overlord. Collect 3 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2783.name: Lakin's Mace
2783.description: Mace used by a lakin. Collect 3 of these to take to Duelist Kaien.

2784.name: Luther's Letter
2784.description: A letter given by Master Luther. Take this to Alex of the village of Floran.

2785.name: Alex's Warrant
2785.description: A warrant written by Alex. Take this to Leirynn.

2786.name: Leirynn's 1st Order
2786.description: A list of orders given by Leirynn. "Slay 10 Delu Shamans and bring back their tokens."

2787.name: Delu Totem
2787.description: The totem of Shaman Saska. Take this, along with the rest of the Delu Shaman totems, to Leirynn.

2788.name: Leirynn's 2nd Order
2788.description: A list of orders given by Leirynn. Slay Delu chief Kalkis and bring back proof.

2789.name: Chief Kalki's Fang
2789.description: Proof that the Delu chief Kalkis has been slain. Take this to Leirynn.

2790.name: Leirynn's Report
2790.description: A report issued by Leirynn. Take this to Alex.

2791.name: Strange Map
2791.description: A strange map obtained from the Delu chief Kalkis.

2792.name: Lambert's Map
2792.description: A map where the name of Lambert, the former lord's guard, is written.

2793.name: Alex's Letter
2793.description: A letter given by Alex. Take this and go to drunkard Borys at the Town of Gludio.

2794.name: Alex's Order
2794.description: Alex's orders. The orders give instructions to find and recover Duke Ashton's missing gold.

2795.name: Wine Catalog
2795.description: A list of premium wine published by the Giran Traders' Guild. Show this to Trader Tyra.

2796.name: Tyra's Contract
2796.description: The contract that Trader Tyra has drawn up. The contract states that Tyra will trade 10 pouches of red spore dust for a Malrukian wine.

2797.name: Red Spore Dust
2797.description: Red spore dust obtained by slaying the giant fungus. Gather 10 pouches and bring them to Trader Tyra.

2798.name: Malrukian Wine
2798.description: Premium wine crafted following the methods of the Malruk tribe. Take this to drunkard Borys.

2799.name: Old Order
2799.description: An old order received from drunkard Borys. Take this and go to bodyguard Jax.
